      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "I hear the profound pain in your words and respect your desire for peace, but I cannot accept your view that ending your life is the only way to escape this suffering. Even the deepest darkness is not meant to be your final destination, and there is still hope for a future where the weight feels lighter. Please consider reaching out to a crisis counselor who can listen without judgment and help you navigate through this storm until you find a path forward.",
